<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4542125>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 9. Dichotomius fornicatus (Luederwaldt, 1931). A–B. Dorsal habitus. A. ♁. B. ♀. C. Lateral view of the aedeagus. D. Ventral view of the metasternum. Antero-medial edge smooth and shiny, surface near the interior margin of the mesocoxae punctate. E. Ventral view of the aedeagus. F–G. Lamella copulatrix. H. View from above of the head, cephalic carina arcuate." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4542125/files/figure.png" .

