<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4542123>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 8. Dichotomius enioi sp. nov. A–B. Dorsal habitus. A. Holotype, ♁ (CEMT). B. ♀. C. Lateral view of the aedeagus. D. Ocellate punctation of the posterior margin of the pronotum; elytral interstriae shagreened. E. Ventral view of the aedeagus. F–G. Lamella copulatrix. H. Profemur covered with wellimpressed punctures, setigerous setae near the medial edge." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4542123/files/figure.png" .

